@startuml
title ArcHub CMS - Plugin Manifest Lifecycle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor "Plugin developer" as Dev
participant "Plugin manifest\nplugin.json" as Manifest
participant "ArcHubPluginRegistry" as Registry
participant "Knowledge platform" as Platform
participant "Host adapter\nfuture sandbox" as Host

Dev -> Manifest : declare id, version,\ncapability, runtime,\npermissions
Registry -> Manifest : discover from\nARCHUB_PLUGIN_DIRS
Registry -> Registry : validate semver,\ncapability, runtime
Registry --> Platform : catalog and\ncapability matrix
alt trusted runtime binding
  Platform -> Host : bind validated manifest\nto external worker/API
else manifest-only
  Platform --> Platform : expose capability\nwithout code execution
end
@enduml
